item.title: Anxious Tale
item.description: O/|\/\ So in the end, you just stop trying. So in the end, you are always alone.

item.title: Anxious Tale
item.description: O/|\/\ They tell you it's all in your head. But your own head is against you. It's easier to just keep to myself... I'd only be a bother... I'm too shy... I'm too awkward... I'd only look stupid... I'm terrible at talking to people... I don't want to seem clingy... They probably don't want to talk to me anyway... There must be something wrong with me.
